values:
I keep forgetting lj pretty effectively, it seems...
Well, I have nothing to write here anyway really so maybe that's okay then.

I should edit my NaNo. But it's also way too easy to forget somewhere under my bed and then it gets mouldy and I stuff it further in. Out of my sight. Because I can't get anything done now, my BA thesis is dead... That too.

And everything else too for the matter.

I arrived home yesterday from the spring camp. It was lovely (most of the time). So now I'm knackered... Dead tired and still I need to get to uni tomorrow to do my job as an opponent to Oskari. Even if my own thesis is dead atm...

Sigh.

Waredith signing in to report.

Eris just won't let me download Et Cetera Discordia. Stop the discordian propaganda!

That's not what I came here to tell you though.

I just washed my hands. And dried them in my big towel which I've been using for a looong time.
And it stabbed me. I now have a bleeding hole in my thumb.

I am mildly... confused.

...

Yes...

Life is weird and I think the looming end of the world began in may 2010. Probably.
It's not ended yet. But it has begun =) With the slow dying of everything beautiful.

I'm going to buy myself a shirt today, and sew on it with lacey ribbons and glitter the text: 
I AM CIRCUS


Confusion.

I FUCKING OWN SO MUCH GOT 50,000 WORDS ON 23. NOVEMBER DESPITE ALL THE CRAP DURING THE WEEKEND AND MY FINGERS ARE ALL DEAD NOW AND I CAN'T UNDERSTAND A WORDS OF THE STUFF I WROTE ON WRITE OR DIE BUT HELL YEAH 5463 TODAY Now this evening WOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOT!!! TRIPLE WIN FOR THE DISCORDIANS!
First Write or Die evah ^^ And the second:

Last night... 00:00 I started to write. Despite the fact that I'd been celebrating kekri last weekend ==> almost no bloody sleep whatsoever... And then you start writing and agonising and feeling sorry for your FMC and then it's 3 a.m. and you think the desk you're sitting by is floating with a 60 degree angle to the floor... And then... you go home... And at halv past 4...

It is time to go to sleep. Because you reached 104% of your wordcount goal ^^
...and then you dream of people who make you and your friends eat daterapedrugs or smth...


Whoa.

I'm knackered.

Uni soonish. Did anyone see my brain?



EDIT: I got dressed. Brown teaparty dress. White fluffy kneesocks. And a white collarshirt.

I feel like a fucking gingerbread (with a knife).

I need Burning Man... Year 2012: The End of the World... theme ftw.


Only a little over a week till NaNoWriMo... Ofelia, CC... Thou shalt be awakened soon <3 Hopefully you are going to be fun and fucked up, otherwise you die. Yes, that is a threat. And CC, you will get a real name, I promise... ._.

...

I - OFFICIALLY - HATE - LIVEJOURNAL. WHY THE FUCK CAN THEY NOT MAKE IT POSSIBLE FOR NON-NERDS TO ALTER THE COLOUR OF THE BLOODY JOURNAL EASILY AND WITHOUT THE NEED TO GET A STUPID CUSTOM-THINGY FIRST WHICH IS ALL FUCKED UP LAYOUT-WISE AND AND AND... fuck it. I hate this shit.


And the earlier journal from before LJ fucked with my brain:

Abney Park =( Stupid SiS Bolig (the people who I paid my rent to while in Norway) stole me money, so now I has none for Abney goodies... AND I REALLY NEED THEM D'=

I got nuts when I saw who'd made the Saints and Sinners AP cuffs *drooooooool*


Why

Why

...

Why... ='C 

Mates... Give me the last olive cuff and I will not make the world one fcking big lake of tears (because... you know.. that would make it difficult for airships, yes? ...The air... full of water... and various other stuff you have in tears...)

Off to emo now... =C



________________________________________________________________________________

Later:

My lovely god (http://cattness.livejournal.com/) got my password and thus she was able to make my LJ actually nice... Worship her, ye all.

Oh and credit for the layout goes to scholarslayouts...

Hmm... 


Anything to do here?

Nope.

Been painting stuff again. Playing decadent artist with blood in my goblet of wine and weird piccie ^^

Yay


I'm bored

We need to speed up research because we need...
Pet Velociraptor for
Flying DeLorean for
Teleportation Booths for
Talking Cats for
Von Neumann Machines for
Carnivorous hollyhocks for
a pet Dalek for
a TARDS for
Sexy Timelords for
Floo Powder for
and for
Please sign the petition in support of the European Commission's proposed Open Access to Research Results!

Hellooo! ^^^

I'm having headache... crappy...

Agh...

There's still too much to do here =P Too bad I can't download anything *kicks computer*

Sooo...
I know who rules




________________________________________
We know where we live...

Could somebody tell me how to orientate here? =S Livejournal is meeeeessy O.O

Too much Kanjani8 over the internet =] I'm getting stressed...

Yay... I don't know whether I like Livejournal or not...

*hugs (if anyone reads this)*
